#: ../../source/features.rst:2
msgid "Features"
msgstr "功能特性"

#: ../../source/features.rst:5
msgid "Natural Language Interface"
msgstr "自然语言界面"

#: ../../source/features.rst:7
msgid ""
"Describe what you want to do in plain English, and EDAI's LLM agent "
"translates it into the appropriate EDA commands."
msgstr ""
"用简单的英语描述您想要做的事情，EDAI 的 LLM 智能体会将其转换为适当的 EDA 命令。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:16
msgid ""
"The agent maintains conversation context, so you can refine requests "
"iteratively just as you would with a colleague."
msgstr ""
"智能体保持对话上下文，因此您可以像与同事交流一样迭代地优化请求。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:20
msgid "Built-in Tcl Interpreter"
msgstr "内置 Tcl 解释器"

#: ../../source/features.rst:22
msgid ""
"EDAI comes with a Tcl interpreter that understands **184 EDA commands** "
"organized across 19 subsystems. You can type Tcl commands directly "
"without any special prefix:"
msgstr ""
"EDAI 内置一个 Tcl 解释器，支持横跨 19 个子系统的 **184 条 EDA 命令**。您可以直接输入 Tcl 命令，无需任何特殊前缀："

#: ../../source/features.rst:32
msgid ""
"The interpreter supports Tcl variable substitution (``$var``), command "
"substitution (``[command]``), and built-in commands such as ``set``, "
"``puts``, and ``expr``."
msgstr ""
"解释器支持 Tcl 变量替换（``$var``）、命令替换（``[command]``）以及内建命令，如 ``set``、``puts`` 和 ``expr``。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:37
msgid "Simulation Mode"
msgstr "模拟模式"

#: ../../source/features.rst:39
msgid ""
"No EDA tool license? No problem. EDAI includes a simulation backend that "
"produces realistic output for all supported commands. This lets you:"
msgstr ""
"没有 EDA 工具许可证？没问题。EDAI 包含一个模拟后端，可为所有支持的命令生成逼真的输出。这使您可以："

#: ../../source/features.rst:43
msgid "**Prototype and debug flows** without touching licensed tools."
msgstr "**原型设计和调试流程**，无需接触许可工具。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:44
msgid "**Learn the tool command set** interactively."
msgstr "**交互式学习工具命令集**。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:45
msgid "**Demonstrate and teach** in environments without tool access."
msgstr "**演示和教学**，在没有工具访问权限的环境中。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:46
msgid "**Test flow scripts** before running them on real tools."
msgstr "**测试流程脚本**，在实际工具上运行之前。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:48
msgid ""
"When connected to a real EDA tool backend, the simulation layer is "
"transparently replaced with live execution."
msgstr ""
"当连接到真实的 EDA 工具后端时，模拟层会被透明地替换为实时执行。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:52
msgid "IPython Shell"
msgstr "IPython Shell"

#: ../../source/features.rst:54
msgid "The full IPython experience is available alongside EDA commands:"
msgstr "完整的 IPython 体验与 EDA 命令并行可用："

#: ../../source/features.rst:56
msgid "Python REPL with history, tab completion, and magic commands."
msgstr "Python REPL，带有历史记录、Tab 补全和魔术命令。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:57
msgid "Rich display of Python objects (DataFrames, arrays, plots)."
msgstr "Python 对象的丰富显示（DataFrame、数组、图表）。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:58
msgid "Access to the Tcl interpreter state from Python."
msgstr "从 Python 访问 Tcl 解释器状态。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:59
msgid "Ability to write Python scripts that mix EDA commands with analysis code."
msgstr "能够编写混合了 EDA 命令和分析代码的 Python 脚本。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:62
msgid ""
"You can query simulation results, compute metrics, or generate reports — "
"all within the same terminal session."
msgstr ""
"您可以查询模拟结果、计算指标或生成报告——所有这些都在同一个终端会话中完成。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:66
msgid "180+ Commands Across the Full EDA Flow"
msgstr "覆盖完整 EDA 流程的 180 多条命令"

#: ../../source/features.rst:68
msgid ""
"The built-in command database covers the major stages of a digital design"
" flow:"
msgstr ""
"内置命令数据库覆盖了数字设计流程的主要阶段："

