msgstr "``report_db``、``report_wirelength``、``report_congestion``"

#: ../../source/features.rst:113
msgid "Tab Completion for Tcl Commands"
msgstr "Tcl 命令的 Tab 补全"

#: ../../source/features.rst:115
msgid "When typing in Tcl mode, you get context-aware tab completion:"
msgstr "在 Tcl 模式下输入时，您可以获得上下文感知的 Tab 补全："

#: ../../source/features.rst:117
msgid "Command name completion — type ``pla`` + :kbd:`Tab` → ``run_placer``."
msgstr "命令名称补全——输入 ``pla`` + :kbd:`Tab` → ``run_placer``。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:118
msgid ""
"Option completion — after a command, :kbd:`Tab` shows available flags "
"like ``-path``, ``-max_density``."
msgstr ""
"选项补全——在命令后按 :kbd:`Tab`，显示可用的标志，如 ``-path``、``-max_density``。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:120
msgid "File path completion — for options expecting file paths."
msgstr "文件路径补全——针对需要文件路径的选项。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:121
msgid "Duplicate option prevention — already-used options are filtered out."
msgstr "重复选项预防——已使用的选项会被过滤掉。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:125
msgid "Configurable LLM Backend"
msgstr "可配置的 LLM 后端"

#: ../../source/features.rst:127
msgid ""
"EDAI works with any OpenAI-compatible API. Configure the model, endpoint,"
" and API key through environment variables:"
msgstr ""
"EDAI 可与任何兼容 OpenAI 的 API 配合使用。通过环境变量配置模型、端点和 API 密钥："

#: ../../source/features.rst:130
msgid "``LLM_BASE_URL`` — API endpoint (defaults to DeepSeek)."
msgstr "``LLM_BASE_URL``——API 端点（默认使用 DeepSeek）。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:131
msgid "``LLM_MODEL_ID`` — model identifier."
msgstr "``LLM_MODEL_ID``——模型标识符。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:132
msgid "``LLM_API_KEY`` — your API key."
msgstr "``LLM_API_KEY``——您的 API 密钥。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:134
msgid ""
"This makes it easy to switch between cloud providers or use a locally-"
"hosted model."
msgstr ""
"这使得在云提供商之间切换或使用本地托管的模型变得非常容易。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:138
msgid "Extensible Tool System"
msgstr "可扩展的工具系统"

#: ../../source/features.rst:140
msgid ""
"Behind the scenes, EDAI has a plugin-style tool architecture. The tool "
"system supports:"
msgstr ""
"在底层，EDAI 采用插件式的工具架构。工具系统支持："

#: ../../source/features.rst:143
msgid "**Bash execution** — run arbitrary shell commands."
msgstr "**Bash 执行**——运行任意 shell 命令。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:144
msgid ""
"**REPL interaction** — interact with persistent subprocesses (Python, "
"Tcl, or custom interpreters)."
msgstr ""
"**REPL 交互**——与持久性子进程（Python、Tcl 或自定义解释器）进行交互。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:146
msgid "**Named interpreters** — spawn and manage long-running language backends."
msgstr "**命名解释器**——生成并管理长时间运行的语言后端。"

#: ../../source/features.rst:149
msgid ""
"New tools can be added without modifying core code, making EDAI adaptable"
" to different EDA toolchains and workflows."
msgstr ""
"无需修改核心代码即可添加新工具，使 EDAI 能够适应不同的 EDA 工具链和工作流程。"
